name: Salesforce Case SLO - Slack Milestones Alerts
description:
**Trigger**: When a case is new/updated and "SLO Alert Message" field is not empty, capture the content from field

**Description**: As a Support Engineer, SLO warning and breach alerts to CaseBot should be aligned with the email notifications in Salesforce that milestones will implement.

**Actions**: Pull the data from SLO Alert Message when it gets updated by milestones and format according to slack format and send it to their respective case owner.
